name: NFTP Search tool
description:
NFT-people audit tool! Search, sort, and find your avatars based on rarity scores and prices!
This tool is available for free use on our website (www.nftpeople.xyz/collect) and minted here as an NFT for free use on Hicetnunc, too.
If you enjoy our project and find this tool handy, you can purchase one of the editions for supporting our future projects! 

This is from Ferio and NFThead to all NFT enthusiasts and Tezos lovers...


Love you all, and enjoy your Tezos punks.
